post_summaries.description: The image shows two mini tortillas topped with a tofu scramble, sliced avocado, and a drizzle of hot sauce. The scramble appears to contain diced red bell peppers. The tortillas are arranged on a bright blue plate.

The image shows a plate of vegan brownies, likely homemade, with a Christmas tree and snowflake ornament in the background. The post mentions it's the first time the poster made this recipe and that they are delicious.
The image shows a slice of homemade vegan "Chx" (chicken) pot pie on a green plate. The pot pie has a flaky crust and a creamy, savory filling with vegetables.

The image shows a box filled with vegan donuts and croissants. There are chocolate-covered donuts, a donut with cookie-like crumbles on top, and croissants, some with powdered sugar and almond slivers.
The image shows a close-up shot of a vegan Caesar salad from Parlor City Vegan. The salad includes greens, grilled bread, what appears to be vegan chicken, carrots, radishes, and a dressing.

The image shows a colorful bowl filled with a vegan breakfast parfait. It includes sliced mango, banana, strawberries, raspberries, vanilla bean cashew yogurt (from Trader Joe's), and homemade granola (recipe from @ohsheglows).
